{"id": 243375948, "title": "Handcuffs on 24-year-old for arson of a vehicle", "text": "In the course of investigating a car arson case and gathering evidence, the police arrested a 24-year-old resident of Limassol to assist with the inquiries. Specifically, on March 9, 2024, the Police received a report of a fire in a vehicle belonging to a 26-year-old in a Limassol area. The Fire Department extinguished the fire, which completely destroyed the vehicle. During the investigation, it was determined that the fire was deliberately set. As part of the probe, testimony emerged against the arrested individual, who was also wanted under a judicial arrest warrant. Limassol CID continues its investigations.", "summary": "In the course of investigating a car arson case and gathering evidence, the police arrested a 24-year-old resident of Limassol to assist with the inquiries. Specifically, on March 9, 2024, the Police received a report of a fire in a vehicle belonging to a 26-year-old in a Limassol area. The Fire Department extinguished the fire, [&#8230;]", "url": "https://in-cyprus.philenews.com/local/handcuffs-on-24-year-old-for-arson-of-a-vehicle/", "image": "https://in-cyprus.philenews.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/police.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-29 06:43:05", "author": "newsroom", "authors": ["newsroom"], "language": "en", "source_country": "cy", "sentiment": -0.926}